Package: CullenFreyX
Type: Package
Title: Statistical Analysis with Cullen and Frey Graph
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Ana Cristina Miranda Cortes
Maintainer: Ana Cristina Miranda Cortes <aniusk898@gmail.com>
Description: A package for statistical analysis including skewness and kurtosis calculations, and the visualization of Cullen and Frey graphs for assessing distribution fit. Provides functions to calculate statistical moments, generate bootstrap samples, and visualize results interactively using Shiny.
